---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="About | Eckman Designs" description="Meet the designer behind Eckman Designs.">
  <section class="py-14 sm:py-18">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs tracking-widest text-navy-900/50">ABOUT</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-navy-900 sm:text-5xl">
          A personal approach to fine jewelry.
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-navy-900/70">
          Eckman Designs is a family-run fine jewelry studio led by Yvette and Garret Eckman, specializing in custom pieces that feel timeless, refined, and deeply personal.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-navy-900/70">
          With over 30 years of experience, Yvette brings an expert eye for craftsmanship, proportion, and stone selection. Together with Garret, she works closely with each client to create jewelry defined by precision, intention, and lasting beauty.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-navy-900/70">
          Every piece begins with a conversationâ€”your story, your style, and the details that matter most.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="rounded-full bg-navy-800 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-soft hover:bg-navy-700"
          >
            Book a Consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/"
            class="rounded-full border border-navy-900/15 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-navy-900 hover:border-navy-900/25"
          >
            View Work
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-6 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-b from-champagne/35 to-transparent blur-2xl"></div>

        <figure class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] border border-black/5 bg-white shadow-soft">
          <img
            src="/images/about-us.jpg"
            alt="Eckman Designs team photo"
            class="h-[520px] w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption class="border-t border-black/5 bg-white px-6 py-4 text-sm text-navy-900/70">
            Crafting custom pieces with care, start to finish.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
